LOCATION:No. 30\, Lane 770\, Bei’an Road\, Zhongshan District\, Taipei\, Taiwan
DESCRIPTION:Joint opening reception for two solos: 王公澤 Whispers of Being / 橫溝美由紀 Landscape—Tracing the Invisible Route (both run to Aug 8). Reception hour unpublished — call 02-8501-2138\; gallery receptions here are typically Saturday afternoon.
