BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:testproject3-20260704@taipei-field-notes
DTSTAMP:20260703T070156Z
SUMMARY:Test Project #3 — TW×JP modular synth + VJ live
LOCATION:No. 23\, Lane 100\, Section 1\, Longmi Road\, Bali District\, New Taipei City\, Taiwan
DESCRIPTION:Cross-national modular-synth afternoon: 5 Japan + 5 Taiwan artists (Syncsick\, Gray Fover\, Paterson\, Su-Ning\, Dei Chi) with synced VJ visuals. NT$800 presale / 900 door. Scene-networking gold for a hardware builder. Last entry 17:30.
DTSTART;TZID=Asia/Taipei:20260704T140000
DTEND;TZID=Asia/Taipei:20260704T180000
END:VEVENT
