BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:tenderfoot-eurorack-20260718@taipei-field-notes
DTSTAMP:20260703T070156Z
SUMMARY:MODULAR SYNTHESIS — Tenderfoot Electronics × Peter Young
LOCATION:No. 28\, Section 2\, Daguan Road\, Banqiao District\, New Taipei City\, Taiwan
DESCRIPTION:Lecture + live demo by Peter Young\, founder of Taiwan Eurorack maker Tenderfoot Electronics: module design\, instrument development\, hands-on sound creation. At NTUA’s sound-art/acoustics research center. Register via Accupass (show app ticket). Same day as LSF #145 (evening) — great double bill.
DTSTART;TZID=Asia/Taipei:20260718T140000
DTEND;TZID=Asia/Taipei:20260718T160000
END:VEVENT
